{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hans came into my classroom because he'd had pretty much the same experience as I did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe because I was a year older than he, he thought I was also a year wiser.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked me, you know, what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said Hans, you go back to your classroom, sit at your desk, and study.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, no, I'm scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can I stay here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, all right, you can stay here, but you have to be quiet because I'm studying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then Hans said, well can I go over and look out the window?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, yes, you can do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you must be quiet now because I'm studying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Hans stood by the window, I don't know, maybe an hour or an hour and a half when he all off the sudden became very excited and he said, come here.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Who are these people?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what we saw were men and boys being marched down the street, four in a row, chained to each other, chained to the ones in front of them, chained to the ones behind them, with SS men hitting them with whips and urging them to walk faster.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know who they were because the school sat back from the road quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we somehow knew, even though we didn't know who they were, that they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with that, we decided we'd better call home and find out what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went next door to a bookstore where there was a phone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I called my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a strange voice answered and said, the phone is no longer in service.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
